      • relocateModuleInsts

        public static boolean relocateModuleInsts(Design top,
                                          Module mod,
                                          String cellAnchor,
                                          List<Pair<String,String>> blackboxes)
        Fill some black boxes of the given design with the given implementation.
        Parameters:
        top - The design with black boxes to fill
        mod - The implementation to fill the black boxes
        cellAnchor - The reference INT tile used as the handle to mod parameter
        blackboxes - The list of pairs of a black box cell to be filled and its reference INT tile. The x-coordinate of this INT tile must match that of the cellAnchor.
